{
  "id": "66cea9fca4fbf8001dfdfa23",
  "title": "夢阿満",
  "created": 1724819966,
  "updated": 1724819966,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "66cea9fca4fbf8001dfdfa23",
      "text": "夢阿満",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a19f",
      "text": " [菅原道真]の[漢詩]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1a0",
      "text": " 　亡くなった子([阿満])を[夢]に見る",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1a1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1a2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1a3",
      "text": "[井上哲次郎] 著『菅原道真』,北海出版社,1936. 国立国会図書館デジタルコレクション https://dl.ndl.go.jp/pid/1874341/1/81 (参照 2023-08-10)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1a4",
      "text": "こちらをもとに書き下し文にしてみる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1a5",
      "text": " 旧字体は現代の漢字に直す",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1a7",
      "text": "阿満の亡せしより来夜眠られず、偶ま眠るも夢に遇ふて涕連々たり、",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1a8",
      "text": "身長は去夏三尺余り、歯立ちて今春七年ばかりなり、",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1a9",
      "text": "事に従って人子の道を知らんと請ひ、書を読み暗誦す[帝京篇]、",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1aa",
      "text": "薬の[況痛]を治むること僅に[旬日]のみ、風は[遊魂]を引く是[九泉]、",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1ab",
      "text": "爾後神を怨み兼て仏を恨む、当初は地も無く又天も無し、",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1ac",
      "text": "吾が両膝を看て多く嘲弄せり、汝の同胞を悼むに共葬すること鮮なし、",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1ad",
      "text": "[莱誕]は珠を含んで老[蚌]を悲しみ、[荘周]は[蛻]を委して[寒蝉]に泣く、",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1ae",
      "text": "なんぞ堪へん[小妹]の名を呼びて覓むるに、忍び難し[阿嬢]の性を滅して憐れむを、",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1af",
      "text": "始は謂へり微微として腸暫く続くと、何に因りてか急急痛きこと煎るが如し、",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1b0",
      "text": "[桑弧]の戸上に[蓬矢]を加え、[竹馬]の[籬頭]に[葛鞭]を着く、",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1b1",
      "text": "庭に駐む栽花の[旧種]、壁に残す学点字の傍辺、",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1b2",
      "text": "毎に言笑を思ひて在るが如しと雖も、希に見る起居惣べて惘然たり、",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1b3",
      "text": "到る処に須く彌百億に迷ひ、生時の世界三千より暗し、",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1b4",
      "text": "南無観自在菩薩、吾が児を擁護して大蓮に座せしめよ。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    },
    {
      "id": "66cea9ff5e90c00000f5a1b5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1724819966,
      "updated": 1724819966
    }
  ]
}